---
title: Pork Schnitzels & Creamy Lemon-Herb Sauce with Dukkah Wedges & Apple Salad
description: All the classic flavours in this German-inspired dish play off against each other in the most delightful way. The sweetness of the
apple with irresistible dukkah-spiced wedges and crunchy panko-coated pork is just lovely!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/classic-pork-schnitzel-creamy-lemon-herb-sauce-67568bdf.jpg
